@startuml
!include ../common/style.puml
title Diagramme de cas d'usage - Fournisseur
left to right direction

actor Fournisseur

rectangle "Plateforme B2B FMCG Export" {
  usecase "S'inscrire fournisseur" as UC_Register
  usecase "Se connecter" as UC_Login
  usecase "Completer fiche societe" as UC_Profile
  usecase "Soumettre documents legaux" as UC_LegalDocs
  usecase "Gerer produits" as UC_ManageProducts
  usecase "Creer produit" as UC_CreateProduct
  usecase "Modifier produit" as UC_UpdateProduct
  usecase "Importer produits en masse" as UC_BulkImport
  usecase "Mettre a jour stocks" as UC_Stocks
  usecase "Gerer grilles tarifaires" as UC_Pricing
  usecase "Consulter RFQ recues" as UC_ViewRFQ
  usecase "Repondre RFQ" as UC_ReplyRFQ
  usecase "Envoyer message" as UC_Message
  usecase "Consulter statistiques fournisseur" as UC_Stats
  usecase "Acheter sponsoring" as UC_Sponsoring
}

Fournisseur --> UC_Register
Fournisseur --> UC_Profile
Fournisseur --> UC_ManageProducts
Fournisseur --> UC_ViewRFQ
Fournisseur --> UC_Stats

UC_Register ..> UC_LegalDocs : <<include>>
UC_ManageProducts ..> UC_Login : <<include>>
UC_CreateProduct ..> UC_ManageProducts : <<include>>
UC_UpdateProduct ..> UC_ManageProducts : <<include>>
UC_BulkImport ..> UC_ManageProducts : <<include>>
UC_Stocks ..> UC_ManageProducts : <<include>>
UC_Pricing ..> UC_ManageProducts : <<include>>
UC_ReplyRFQ ..> UC_ViewRFQ : <<include>>

UC_Message ..> UC_ReplyRFQ : <<extend>>
UC_Sponsoring ..> UC_Stats : <<extend>>

@enduml
